data.value:
***How do I win?*** By playing smart and playing fast; the player with the highest answer and the shortest time wins the top prize of being a contestant on the television show while the subsequent four (4) get to by-pass the verification stage.
***How do I get help if I have an idea about the answer but not sure?*** Here, you can use any of the three available lifelines - “Fifty-Fifty”, “Phone-a-friend” and “Ask the Audience”.
***How many 'Ask the Audience' keypads are there?*** There is a keypad for every member of the audience, the studio seats over 100 people.
***How many “Phone-A-Friend” friends am I allowed?*** You may select up to five friends. We advise that you select ‘friends’ that can assist you in different areas of general knowledge.
